01:01:31.376 --> 01:01:33.253
If the culprit thinks I'm your man,

01:01:33.837 --> 01:01:34.796
I'll either die…

01:01:36.507 --> 01:01:38.175
or find out who the real culprit is.

01:01:38.258 --> 01:01:40.135
What if you really die?

01:01:40.219 --> 01:01:41.220
I don't care.

01:01:41.303 --> 01:01:42.596
Go ahead and use me.

01:01:43.680 --> 01:01:45.682
This isn't over

01:01:46.475 --> 01:01:48.018
until we catch the killer.

01:01:48.685 --> 01:01:50.604
They'll show up in front of me soon

01:01:50.687 --> 01:01:51.939
because I'm Han Seol-ah's man

01:01:52.564 --> 01:01:54.024
who knows their secret.

01:01:55.484 --> 01:01:57.486
